#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn1.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Naḷavagga "
msgstr "1. A Reed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn1.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Nimokkhasutta "
msgstr "2. Liberation "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.2, pts2ed1.3, sc1
msgctxt "sn1.2:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn1.2:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā devatā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then, late at night, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, and said to him, "

#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn1.2:2.1"
msgid "“Jānāsi no tvaṃ, mārisa, sattānaṃ nimokkhaṃ pamokkhaṃ vivekan”ti? "
msgstr "“Good sir, do you understand liberation, emancipation, and seclusion for sentient beings?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn1.2:3.1"
msgid "“Jānāmi khvāhaṃ, āvuso, sattānaṃ nimokkhaṃ pamokkhaṃ vivekan”ti. "
msgstr "“I do, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn1.2:4.1"
msgid "“Yathākathaṃ pana tvaṃ, mārisa, jānāsi sattānaṃ nimokkhaṃ pamokkhaṃ vivekan”ti? "
msgstr "“But how is it that you understand liberation, emancipation, and seclusion for sentient beings?” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.4, sc5
#. VAR: Nandībhavaparikkhayā → nandibhavaparikkhayā (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn1.2:5.1"
msgid "“Nandībhavaparikkhayā, "
msgstr "“With the ending of relish for rebirth, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.2:5.2"
msgid "Saññāviññāṇasaṅkhayā; "
msgstr "the finishing of perception and consciousness, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.2:5.3"
msgid "Vedanānaṃ nirodhā upasamā, "
msgstr "and the cessation and stilling of feelings: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.2:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ khvāhaṃ āvuso jānāmi; "
msgstr "that, sir, is how I understand liberation, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn1.2:5.5"
msgid "Sattānaṃ nimokkhaṃ pamokkhaṃ vivekan”ti. "
msgstr "emancipation, and seclusion for sentient beings.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
